{
  "stem": "17044.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I start to wear the blue arm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They give us to wear patch, one in the front and one in the back, about three inches yellow patch.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And every time a [INAUDIBLE] was they give orders, always they made us in the holidays.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The holidays.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always in the holidays.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Like-- like they're fighting with the-- with guard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You asked me before what did my people-- my parents believed and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody could believe things like this can happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before the war, at least when a pogrom-- a pogrom or something, we used to run to dignitaries and begging for help and everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Here, this time we went to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The answer was, God punish you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You sinners, and God punish you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we want to vent to the Jewish leaders and to the religious rabbis asking for question, why it's happened to us?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why should I have some suffer?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why is the righteous people suffering, et cetera?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they answer, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The righteous suffer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They have to suffer for the better of people, always have those excuses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[SIGHS] ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the meantime, in the town people see is not well and nothing will help.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were talking to escape to the forest because the Germans used to kill the prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These prisoners of war escaped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Instead, to go in prison, they rather escape then live in the forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They start organized already resistance by little groups, Jewish people too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, being in our ghetto, we tried to accumulate weapon and money and to be organized around the forest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was before when the people said, where are we going?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Die in-- in the forest in the winter?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "May as well we'll die in the same in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked on a farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
